23">后来他撤回</a>），并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-releases-new-song-beauty-and-the-beast-before-stripping-yeezy-site-to-only-sell-swastika-t-shirt-3836729">试图通过他的Yeezy网站出售带有魔术师的T恤</a>。最近， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-asks-jewellers-to-design-a-swastika-chain-for-him-3842494">韦斯特（West）要求珠宝商使他成为一个带有swastika吊坠的连锁店</a>。</p><p>他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-teases-sunday-service-return-then-posts-photo-of-kkk-robe-3844826">取笑了他的福音集团周日服务的归来，然后开玩笑说他的“每日服装”是Ku Klux Klan Hooded Cloak</a> 。</p><p>在其他新闻中，你们仍然卷入法律问题。你们透露<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kim-kardashian-and-kanye-west-at-war-after-he-drops-song-seemingly-featuring-diddy-and-their-daughter-north-3846591">，他准备与前妻金·卡戴珊（Kim Kardashian）在商标上“战争”，以其长女的名字西北，</a>因此他可以与她一起发行“ <a href="/diddy">Diddy</a> Song”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tde-punch-kanye-west-comments-kendrick-lamar-playboi-carti-music-album-3846346">TDE Punch帖子对Kanye West对Kendrick Lamar的最新评论做出了回应，</a>该评论首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
